HOME.ONE_TIME_SECRET_MESSAGING_SUBTITLE: Tāpiri tūmataiti, ā, ka ngaro—kāore e kitea!
HOME.ENCRYPTED_PROTECTED_BY: Kia whakamarūhia, whakawhāiti, ā, tiakina e Stellar Security
HOME.WITHOUT_TRACE_DESCRIPTION: Ka mōhiotia e mātou te tiaki kaha o tō mōhiohio pēnei. Katoa ngā raraunga e whakamōhiotia ana i runga i te taha kiritaki. Kāore e mōhiotia e mātou tō IP wāhitau, he aha tāu e tohatoha ana, ā, nā wai e tohatoha ana i ngā hono tūmataiti - ā, te mea nui, te kōrero.
HOME.PRIVACY_PROTECTED_DESCRIPTION: Ko koe anake e mōhio ana ki te hono ki ngā mōhiohio tūmataiti i hangaia e koe me nā wai e tohatoha ana. I te waihanga i te tūmataiti, ka taea e koe te tāpiri i te kupu huna i mua i te taea te whakatuwhera. Ka taea hoki te tautuhi i te wā kāinga. Ahakoa te aha, ka mōhiotia te tūmataiti i muri i ngā rā 14.
HOME.END_TO_END_ENCRYPTED_TITLE: Whakamōhiotia i runga i te taha katoa
HOME.END_TO_END_ENCRYPTED_DESCRIPTION: Katoa ngā hono me ngā kōrero e hangaia ana i runga i te taha kiritaki, ā, ahakoa kāore mātou e mōhio ana ki te hono me te kōrero. Kāore e whai ID ahurei o te roa 36 mō ia hono he whakamōhiotanga kotahi hei āhei ki te uru ki te Tūmataiti Kōrero me te kōrero e whakamōhiotia ana me AES-256.
